OL,3,CZara ads banned for 'irresponsible'
OL,4,Cuse of models who looked 'unhealthily
OL,5,Cthin'
OL,7,FHigh street fashion retailer Zara has
OL,8,Fbeen labelled "socially irresponsible"
OL,9,Fby the advertising watchdog after it
OL,10,Fused photos of models who appeared to
OL,11,Fbe unhealthily thin to advertise its
OL,12,Fclothes.
OL,14,FThe two product listings on the Zara
OL,15,Fwebsite in May featured an image of a
OL,16,Fmodel wearing an oversized pocket
OL,17,Fshirt and another of a model wearing a
OL,18,Fvoluminous combined short dress.
