OL,3,CZara ads banned for 'irresponsible'
OL,4,Cuse of models who looked 'unhealthily
OL,5,Cthin'
OL,7,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,8,F(ASA) received one complaint that the
OL,9,Fads were irresponsible because the
OL,10,Fmodels appeared to be unhealthily thin.
OL,12,FZara said the models had worked for
OL,13,Fwell-known and reputable fashion
OL,14,Fbrands and confirmed that both models
OL,15,Fhad medical certification, which
OL,16,Fproved they were in good health.
OL,18,FThey said that none of the images had
OL,19,Fbeen modified, beyond very minor
OL,20,Flighting and colouring edits.
