OL,7,FThe ASA said: "Overall, we considered
OL,8,Fthat the pose of the model and the
OL,9,Fchoice of clothing in the ad created
OL,10,Fthe impression that the model was
OL,11,Funhealthily thin."
OL,13,FThe watchdog said the styling and
OL,14,Flighting of the second image and the
OL,15,Fchoice of clothing meant the ad
OL,16,Fcreated the impression that the model
OL,17,Fwas also unhealthily thin.
